title: Number of Qdoba restaurants from 2011 to 2017
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Franchise, and Company-owned. The y axis denotes Number of restaurants and the x axis denotes Year.
Overall Company-owned is gradually increasing, Franchise is roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The lines ordered according to average values of Number of restaurants in descending order is: 1. Franchise, and lastly, 2. Company-owned.
Overall across the Year, Franchise mostly maintained the highest Number of restaurants when compared to others with a mean value of 329.71, and it peaked at 2017.
The botommost line, Company-owned,  has a mean of 320.14, and peaked at 2017.
